						<summary>

						<p>Slab on the boundary between Muttalūrpāḍu and Miḍutūru in a field.</p>						

						<p>This is dated in the cyclic year Vikṛiti, Māgha.</p>						

						<p>It states that the stone marks the boundary on the east side between Miḍutūru and two other villages.</p>						

						</summary>
